theorem Topology.closureInterior_union
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X} :
    closure (interior (A ∪ B)) = closure (interior A) ∪ closure (interior B) := by
  calc
    closure (interior (A ∪ B))
        = closure (interior A ∪ interior B) := by
          simpa [interior_union]
    _   = closure (interior A) ∪ closure (interior B) := by
          simpa using closure_union

theorem Topology.closureInterior_union_subset
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X} :
    closure (interior A) ∪ closure (interior B) ⊆
      closure (interior (A ∪ B)) := by
  intro x hx
  rcases hx with hxA | hxB
  ·
    have h_int : (interior A : Set X) ⊆ interior (A ∪ B) := by
      intro y hy
      exact Or.inl hy
    have h_closure : closure (interior A) ⊆ closure (interior (A ∪ B)) :=
      closure_mono h_int
    exact h_closure hxA
  ·
    have h_int : (interior B : Set X) ⊆ interior (A ∪ B) := by
      intro y hy
      exact Or.inr hy
    have h_closure : closure (interior B) ⊆ closure (interior (A ∪ B)) :=
      closure_mono h_int
    exact h_closure hxB

theorem Topology.interiorClosure_subset_interiorClosure_union_left
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X} :
    interior (closure (A : Set X)) ⊆ interior (closure (A ∪ B)) := by
  have h_subset : (A : Set X) ⊆ (A ∪ B) := by
    intro x hx
    exact Or.inl hx
  exact
    Topology.interiorClosure_mono (X := X) (A := A) (B := A ∪ B) h_subset
